    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s in gorgeous, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it still has that 'new car' smell. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
