      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit boasts individual throttle bodies and a high-compression ratio, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The double-VANOS variable valve timing system has been overhauled for precision, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute, with the rear subframe mounting points professionally reinforced. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these cars are known for. Every mechanical component operates in perfect synchronicity, making this a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
