    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a breathtaking 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman that can only be described as being in showroom-fresh condition. This vehicle has been meticulously curated by a single enthusiast owner and kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The Jet Black Metallic paint is flawless, having undergone a professional paint correction followed by a premium ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish with zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the black leather sport seats show no signs of compression or bolster wear, and the factory floor mats remain pristine. Every electronic component, from the Bose Surround Sound system to the PCM navigation, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history documented exclusively through Porsche dealerships. It has never seen rain, let alone salt, and the undercarriage remains as clean as the top side. This sale includes the original window sticker, two keys, and a comprehensive binder of all service records. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
